  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/03/21/blackberry-sells-most-canadian-real-estate/\"><img alt=\"BlackBerry's John Chen at Mobile World Congress\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/f048d43020b99971caabb2efc14bf27c/blackberry-john-chen-crop.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 339px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n几周前我们就感受到了 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/20/blackberry-q3-earnings-huge-loss-foxconn-partnership/\">BlackBerry</a> 计划卖出加拿大房产换取现金的信号，而如今这果然变成了现实。据悉他们今天已与相关方面达成了协议，卖出了旗下超过 300 万平方英尺的房产。在此之后，BlackBerry 将以租客身份回租，所以说其总部应该能保留完整。如果计划顺利的话，交易应该能在 BlackBerry 本财季结束前完成（差不多在五月）。这样一来他们应该能更专注于自己的核心业务，比如说，去劝劝<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/21/white-house-smartphone/\">白宫</a>回心转意什么的...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/21/blackberry-sells-most-canadian-real-estate/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-03-21/blackberry-agrees-to-sell-most-of-canada-real-estate-holdings.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bloomberg</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://press.blackberry.com/press/2014/blackberry-announces-update-on-sale-of-canadian--real-estate-hol.html\" target=\"_blank\">BlackBerry</a></span><br />\n更多信息：<span class=\"more-coverage\"><a href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/blackberry-to-divest-real-estate-holdings/article16438372/\" target=\"_blank\">The Globe and Mail</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/21/blackberry-sells-most-canadian-real-estate/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20854516/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.